item.description:
In order to control the keyboard and mouse of your computer remotely via SSH follow the following steps.
  SSH into your system with X tunning enabled by putting &quot;-X&quot; flag at the end of your SSH command &ldquo;ssh &lt;user&gt;@&lt;ip_address&gt; -X&rdquo;
  Install x2x package on your remote computer. If you are running Debian/Ubuntu based distro then type &ldquo;sudo apt install x2x&rdquo; on your remote computer to install the package.
